Package: ipeaData
Type: Package
Title: Package to getting data from IPEADATA
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Gustavo","Coelho", role=c("aut","cre"), email="gustavo.coelho@ipea.gov.br"),
    )
Maintainer: Gustavo Coelho <gustavo.coelho@ipea.gov.br>
Description: Functions to access data from IPEA (Instituto de Pesquisa Economica Aplicada) hosted
             at (http://www.ipeadata.gov.br/). It gets metadata and values for all series on 
             the website.
